1
00:00:46,840 --> 00:00:47,600
Yun Yuan.

2
00:00:51,080 --> 00:00:51,600
Di Yun.

3
00:00:52,960 --> 00:00:53,690
You're back.

4
00:00:54,040 --> 00:00:55,900
Did you find a way to save Ling'er?

5
00:00:55,920 --> 00:00:57,600
Your Highness, who is this?

6
00:00:58,360 --> 00:00:59,640
I invited Lord Yanxi.

7
00:00:59,760 --> 00:01:01,560
He can definitely cure Ling'er.

8
00:01:03,440 --> 00:01:04,480
What happened?

9
00:01:05,840 --> 00:01:06,880
It's nothing.

10
00:01:07,360 --> 00:01:08,440
Lord Yanxi,

11
00:01:08,480 --> 00:01:10,140
please take a look at Ling'er.

12
00:01:10,520 --> 00:01:11,560
I'd be grateful, my Lord.

13
00:01:11,560 --> 00:01:12,760
Go check on my Ling...

14
00:01:14,640 --> 00:01:16,240
check on this friend of mine.

15
00:01:16,320 --> 00:01:17,680
Your Highness, please don't rush.

16
00:01:17,680 --> 00:01:19,280
Let me take a look first,

17
00:01:19,280 --> 00:01:20,940
then I will report back to you.

18
00:01:21,960 --> 00:01:22,760
Please.

19
00:01:39,960 --> 00:01:42,160
The poison and curse in this girl must be resolved simultaneously.

20
00:01:42,160 --> 00:01:43,920
If we only resolve one of them,

21
00:01:44,160 --> 00:01:46,160
her soul will scatter immediately.

22
00:01:47,320 --> 00:01:48,560
I can only neutralize the poison.

23
00:01:48,560 --> 00:01:49,490
As for the curse,

24
00:01:49,759 --> 00:01:51,360
unless we know what curse it is,

25
00:01:51,360 --> 00:01:52,560
there is no solution.

26
00:01:53,080 --> 00:01:55,320
I have trapped Yin Feng in the Universe Cauldron.

27
00:01:55,320 --> 00:01:56,200
Perhaps,

28
00:01:56,440 --> 00:01:57,900
he knows what the curse is.

29
00:01:57,920 --> 00:01:59,160
Then what are we waiting for?

30
00:01:59,160 --> 00:02:00,560
Let him out and interrogate him now!

31
00:02:00,560 --> 00:02:01,360
No.

32
00:02:02,360 --> 00:02:03,960
His words cannot be trusted.

33
00:02:04,040 --> 00:02:06,100
Let him suffer in the cauldron first.

34
00:02:06,840 --> 00:02:08,360
When he is weaker,

35
00:02:08,720 --> 00:02:10,479
I will use the Soul Probing Technique

36
00:02:10,479 --> 00:02:12,480
to check his soul imprint directly.

37
00:02:15,160 --> 00:02:16,360
I can't take the risk.

38
00:02:16,720 --> 00:02:17,400
Ling'er is already...

39
00:02:17,400 --> 00:02:17,760
Alas.

40
00:02:24,360 --> 00:02:27,440
The General and I went to Wanchong Valley to ask the Great Witch for help.

41
00:02:27,440 --> 00:02:29,770
The General's body is severely depleted.

42
00:02:30,160 --> 00:02:32,360
He fought the Demon Tribe after returning.

43
00:02:32,360 --> 00:02:33,960
If the General doesn't rest now,

44
00:02:33,960 --> 00:02:36,760
he won't be able to use the Soul Probing Technique.

45
00:02:42,440 --> 00:02:43,300
Your Highness,

46
00:02:43,320 --> 00:02:45,440
you must take care of yourself too.

47
00:02:45,760 --> 00:02:47,720
You almost damaged your foundation this time.

48
00:02:47,720 --> 00:02:49,120
If you don't get treated,

49
00:02:49,560 --> 00:02:50,280
I'm afraid

50
00:02:50,440 --> 00:02:51,920
you will never recover.

51
00:02:52,680 --> 00:02:53,680
What happened?

52
00:02:53,960 --> 00:02:56,360
Why is His Highness so heavily injured?

53
00:02:56,880 --> 00:02:58,440
To save this girl, His Highness

54
00:02:58,440 --> 00:02:59,880
climbed the Heavenly Ladder.

55
00:02:59,880 --> 00:03:02,560
He narrowly escaped death to return to the Celestial Tribe,

56
00:03:02,560 --> 00:03:03,680
and without a moment's rest,

57
00:03:03,680 --> 00:03:05,360
he dragged me here.

58
00:03:05,520 --> 00:03:06,920
So that's what happened.

59
00:03:08,360 --> 00:03:10,560
Your Highness, please heal your wounds quickly.

60
00:03:10,560 --> 00:03:12,360
Leave the rest to me.

61
00:03:43,320 --> 00:03:44,320
Grand Protector.

62
00:03:44,560 --> 00:03:45,760
Since the Spirit Pearl has appeared,

63
00:03:45,760 --> 00:03:47,160
why don't we seize it?

64
00:03:47,280 --> 00:03:48,079
No rush.

65
00:03:48,720 --> 00:03:50,120
It's not the time yet.

66
00:04:02,160 --> 00:04:04,690
Shi Hun pays respects to the Grand Protector.

67
00:04:07,160 --> 00:04:08,880
King Kunmi hasn't returned from seeking a doctor.

68
00:04:08,880 --> 00:04:10,960
The Dragon Princess is unconscious.

69
00:04:11,640 --> 00:04:12,760
Unconscious?

70
00:04:14,360 --> 00:04:15,040
Li Sha.

71
00:04:15,360 --> 00:04:16,040
My Lord.

72
00:04:16,040 --> 00:04:17,240
Greetings, Demon Lord.

73
00:04:17,240 --> 00:04:18,640
A thousand years ago,

74
00:04:19,240 --> 00:04:22,720
I personally planted a poison curse in the Dragon Princess.

75
00:04:22,880 --> 00:04:24,360
No one can break it.

76
00:04:24,960 --> 00:04:28,720
Hahaha.

77
00:04:31,880 --> 00:04:33,760
He didn't say what poison curse it is.

78
00:04:33,760 --> 00:04:34,420
Could it be,

79
00:04:34,800 --> 00:04:36,060
he doesn't know at all,

80
00:04:36,320 --> 00:04:37,980
and is just trying to survive?

81
00:04:38,080 --> 00:04:39,540
That's why you tricked me.

82
00:04:39,960 --> 00:04:41,020
Let's wait and see.

83
00:04:41,400 --> 00:04:42,440
Grand Guardian.

84
00:04:42,560 --> 00:04:44,360
The poison curse the Demon Lord spoke of,

85
00:04:44,360 --> 00:04:46,360
can it really make the Dragon Princess

86
00:04:46,360 --> 00:04:47,960
willingly give up the Spirit Pearl?

87
00:04:47,960 --> 00:04:49,159
What do you know?

88
00:04:49,880 --> 00:04:51,120
His Lordship's mind

89
00:04:51,159 --> 00:04:52,960
is not for you and me to guess.

90
00:04:53,040 --> 00:04:54,240
I truly do not understand.

91
00:04:54,240 --> 00:04:55,300
I was just curious.

92
00:04:55,840 --> 00:04:57,970
You are the Demon Lord's trusted aide.

93
00:04:58,440 --> 00:05:00,760
I am willing to follow you forever, Grand Guardian.

94
00:05:00,760 --> 00:05:03,360
We all serve His Lordship.

95
00:05:03,720 --> 00:05:05,360
As long as you are loyal,

96
00:05:05,920 --> 00:05:09,280
His Lordship will regard you highly.

97
00:05:10,120 --> 00:05:11,200
My loyalty to the Demon Lord

98
00:05:11,200 --> 00:05:12,480
and to you, Grand Guardian,

99
00:05:12,480 --> 00:05:13,720
is plain for all to see.

100
00:05:13,720 --> 00:05:15,650
Whatever you say, Grand Guardian,

101
00:05:16,160 --> 00:05:18,120
I treat as absolute law.

102
00:05:18,920 --> 00:05:20,440
Oh, you.

103
00:05:23,720 --> 00:05:24,560
Never mind.

104
00:05:24,640 --> 00:05:26,560
I will satisfy your curiosity.

105
00:05:29,280 --> 00:05:31,200
The poison curse His Lordship spoke of

106
00:05:31,200 --> 00:05:33,040
is called Huangquan Biluo.

107
00:05:33,360 --> 00:05:34,560
The poison is Huangquan.

108
00:05:34,560 --> 00:05:35,620
The curse is Biluo.

109
00:05:36,680 --> 00:05:38,120
The poison and curse reinforce each other.

110
00:05:38,120 --> 00:05:38,960
They rise together

111
00:05:38,960 --> 00:05:40,040
and fall together.

112
00:05:42,640 --> 00:05:43,970
The victim of this curse

113
00:05:44,159 --> 00:05:48,080
will have all spiritual power drained in their dreams.

114
00:05:48,840 --> 00:05:51,300
Until their power is exhausted and they die.

115
00:05:51,480 --> 00:05:54,960
Their soul will also be completely eroded.

116
00:05:57,640 --> 00:05:59,040
Such a vicious method.

117
00:06:00,080 --> 00:06:01,610
What kind of grudge is this,

118
00:06:02,160 --> 00:06:04,560
to cast such a terrible curse on Ling'er?

119
00:06:04,680 --> 00:06:05,610
Grand Guardian,

120
00:06:06,080 --> 00:06:08,610
will Huangquan Biluo erode the Spirit Pearl?

121
00:06:08,840 --> 00:06:10,640
If the Spirit Pearl is also destroyed,

122
00:06:10,640 --> 00:06:12,700
wouldn't our loss outweigh the gain?

123
00:06:14,120 --> 00:06:16,050
You don't need to worry about that.

124
00:06:16,120 --> 00:06:17,450
Thousands of years ago,

125
00:06:17,720 --> 00:06:20,440
His Lordship devised a comprehensive plan.

126
00:06:20,920 --> 00:06:22,520
When that Dragon Princess

127
00:06:22,600 --> 00:06:25,120
is eroded away by Huangquan Biluo,

128
00:06:25,560 --> 00:06:27,820
the Spirit Pearl will become ownerless.

129
00:06:27,880 --> 00:06:29,480
His Lordship will return.

130
00:06:29,720 --> 00:06:32,159
Soon, His Lordship will unite the Three Realms

131
00:06:32,159 --> 00:06:33,880
and rule over all.

132
00:06:41,560 --> 00:06:42,360
General.

133
00:06:42,920 --> 00:06:43,920
Well?

134
00:06:46,880 --> 00:06:48,140
It is Huangquan Biluo.

135
00:06:49,520 --> 00:06:51,159
It's actually Huangquan Biluo.

136
00:06:51,159 --> 00:06:53,090
Does Lord Yanxi know of this curse?

137
00:06:54,920 --> 00:06:56,520
This curse was lost long ago.

138
00:06:56,960 --> 00:06:58,960
I have only seen it in ancient books.

139
00:06:59,159 --> 00:07:00,360
The books record that

140
00:07:00,760 --> 00:07:03,560
Huangquan Biluo is the most vicious ancient curse.

141
00:07:03,560 --> 00:07:04,760
Those who fall victim to it

142
00:07:04,760 --> 00:07:06,960
will have their body and soul completely eroded.

143
00:07:06,960 --> 00:07:08,490
Their soul will dissipate.

144
00:07:10,480 --> 00:07:11,340
Your Highness,

145
00:07:11,920 --> 00:07:13,720
forgive my lack of skill.

146
00:07:13,720 --> 00:07:15,050
I cannot save this girl.

147
00:07:15,240 --> 00:07:17,080
Even Lord Yanxi cannot save her?

148
00:07:20,360 --> 00:07:21,220
Your Highness,

149
00:07:21,360 --> 00:07:23,080
Since I am of no help

150
00:07:23,080 --> 00:07:24,360
by staying here,

151
00:07:24,360 --> 00:07:26,360
I will return to the Celestial Clan.

152
00:07:36,159 --> 00:07:37,560
Lord Yanxi, please wait.

153
00:07:41,120 --> 00:07:42,520
You have taken such trouble

154
00:07:42,520 --> 00:07:44,240
coming to my Yunshen to save someone.

155
00:07:44,240 --> 00:07:46,240
I should escort you out personally.

156
00:07:47,000 --> 00:07:47,520
Please.

157
00:08:14,320 --> 00:08:17,250
Please tell me the cure for Huangquan Biluo, my Lord.

158
00:08:17,920 --> 00:08:19,920
King Kunmi, what do you mean by that?

159
00:08:20,480 --> 00:08:21,920
My knowledge is limited.

160
00:08:21,920 --> 00:08:23,650
I cannot cure Huangquan Biluo.

161
00:08:24,240 --> 00:08:25,700
Rest assured, Lord Yanxi.

162
00:08:26,360 --> 00:08:28,080
Our conversation today...

163
00:08:28,360 --> 00:08:30,290
will not be known by a third person.

164
00:08:30,480 --> 00:08:32,080
Especially not Diyun.

165
00:08:35,760 --> 00:08:37,760
I don't know what King Kunmi is talking about.

166
00:08:37,760 --> 00:08:40,559
Your eyes just betrayed you, Lord Yanxi.

167
00:08:40,640 --> 00:08:41,559
I guess...

168
00:08:41,760 --> 00:08:45,020
the cure for Huangquan Biluo must be extremely dangerous.

169
00:08:45,880 --> 00:08:47,540
The reason you won't say it...

170
00:08:47,720 --> 00:08:50,840
is because you fear Diyun will stop at nothing...

171
00:08:50,920 --> 00:08:52,280
and even risk his life.

172
00:08:54,280 --> 00:08:55,080
King Kunmi.

173
00:08:55,760 --> 00:08:57,280
Why do you persist?

174
00:08:57,440 --> 00:08:59,680
Leaving aside whether this method works...

175
00:08:59,680 --> 00:09:00,680
even if it does,

176
00:09:00,760 --> 00:09:03,640
one slip could doom you eternally.

177
00:09:04,720 --> 00:09:07,040
Even if there is only a one in ten thousand chance,

178
00:09:07,040 --> 00:09:08,960
I am willing to bet my life on it.

179
00:09:09,680 --> 00:09:11,010
Please tell me, my Lord.

180
00:09:13,360 --> 00:09:14,160
Very well.

181
00:09:14,240 --> 00:09:16,440
Since King Kunmi insists,

182
00:09:16,760 --> 00:09:18,360
I will tell you.

183
00:09:18,760 --> 00:09:21,200
However, this method...

184
00:09:21,480 --> 00:09:23,720
I have only seen it in ancient texts.

185
00:09:24,120 --> 00:09:25,650
Whether it will succeed...

186
00:09:26,040 --> 00:09:27,760
is unknown even to me.

187
00:09:28,040 --> 00:09:29,570
Please tell me, Lord Yanxi.

188
00:09:30,560 --> 00:09:32,560
Huangquan Biluo indeed has no cure.

189
00:09:32,680 --> 00:09:33,840
In the ancient texts,

190
00:09:33,840 --> 00:09:34,960
there is only one record...

191
00:09:34,960 --> 00:09:37,360
of a desperate method to find life in death.

192
00:09:38,720 --> 00:09:39,640
To be specific,

193
00:09:40,440 --> 00:09:41,760
at the dawn of time,

194
00:09:41,920 --> 00:09:45,960
Heaven and Earth birthed three divine beasts: the Ancestral Dragon, Primordial Phoenix, and Qilin.

195
00:09:45,960 --> 00:09:47,120
During the Primordial War,

196
00:09:47,120 --> 00:09:48,480
the three divine beasts fell.

197
00:09:48,480 --> 00:09:51,160
When the Ancestral Dragon died, it left behind a Seven-Colored Spirit Bead,

198
00:09:51,160 --> 00:09:53,620
guarded by the Dragon Clan for generations.

199
00:09:53,640 --> 00:09:54,440
However,

200
00:09:55,960 --> 00:09:58,040
rumor has it that a thousand years ago,

201
00:09:58,040 --> 00:10:00,300
this Spirit Bead had already shattered.

202
00:10:00,360 --> 00:10:01,360
In other words,

203
00:10:02,320 --> 00:10:03,840
with the Seven-Colored Spirit Bead,

204
00:10:03,840 --> 00:10:05,500
Huangquan Biluo can be cured.

205
00:10:08,240 --> 00:10:09,560
Once you have the Seven-Colored Spirit Bead,

206
00:10:09,560 --> 00:10:11,880
you also need the Seven-Colored Camellia of my Celestial Clan.

207
00:10:11,880 --> 00:10:13,440
Then, using the power of the soul,

208
00:10:13,440 --> 00:10:14,960
use the Qiankun Cauldron to refine the Spirit Bead and

209
00:10:14,960 --> 00:10:17,120
the Camellia into a Seven-Colored Stone.

210
00:10:17,120 --> 00:10:18,980
This might cure Huangquan Biluo.

211
00:10:19,440 --> 00:10:20,900
Seven-Colored Camellia.

212
00:10:22,160 --> 00:10:23,220
Qiankun Cauldron.

213
00:10:24,960 --> 00:10:27,960
The Qiankun Cauldron is a holy relic of the ancient Phoenix Clan.

214
00:10:27,960 --> 00:10:30,080
The Phoenix Clan was wiped out ten thousand years ago.

215
00:10:30,080 --> 00:10:33,360
Since then, there has been no news of the Qiankun Cauldron in this world.

216
00:10:33,360 --> 00:10:35,640
If you want to obtain the Seven-Colored Stone,

217
00:10:35,640 --> 00:10:38,360
the Spirit Bead, the Camellia, and the Qiankun Cauldron...

218
00:10:38,360 --> 00:10:39,840
are all indispensable.

219
00:10:43,040 --> 00:10:44,680
Thank you for telling me, my Lord.

220
00:10:44,680 --> 00:10:47,940
I will refine the Seven-Colored Stone as soon as possible.

221
00:10:52,240 --> 00:10:53,760
Thank you for seeing me off, King Kunmi.

222
00:10:53,760 --> 00:10:55,560
I will take my leave now.

223
00:11:00,480 --> 00:11:01,280
Yueying.

224
00:11:04,160 --> 00:11:04,960
General.

225
00:11:06,080 --> 00:11:07,410
Go and drive Diyun away.

226
00:11:07,960 --> 00:11:08,800
Just say

227
00:11:08,920 --> 00:11:10,520
I only want to be alone with Ling'er.

228
00:11:10,520 --> 00:11:11,780
I don't want to see him.

229
00:11:15,360 --> 00:11:16,220
Your Highness.

230
00:11:16,680 --> 00:11:17,560
You dead fish eyes!

231
00:11:17,560 --> 00:11:18,680
Make it clear to me!

232
00:11:18,720 --> 00:11:19,920
What is the meaning of this?

233
00:11:19,920 --> 00:11:20,960
Why are you doing this?

234
00:11:20,960 --> 00:11:21,820
Your Highness,

235
00:11:21,960 --> 00:11:23,080
just listen to my advice.

236
00:11:23,080 --> 00:11:24,560
Go back and heal your wounds first.

237
00:11:24,560 --> 00:11:25,560
Don't stop me!

238
00:11:26,440 --> 00:11:27,440
Don't think I'm afraid of you.

239
00:11:27,440 --> 00:11:27,960
Di Yun.

240
00:11:30,200 --> 00:11:31,460
I haven't given up yet.

241
00:11:31,560 --> 00:11:32,890
And neither should you.

242
00:11:32,960 --> 00:11:34,240
For the remaining time,

243
00:11:34,240 --> 00:11:36,840
I just want to stay by Ling'er's side properly.

244
00:11:36,920 --> 00:11:37,920
You should leave.

245
00:11:37,960 --> 00:11:39,220
I don't want to see you.

246
00:11:39,760 --> 00:11:40,440
Why?

247
00:11:40,600 --> 00:11:41,640
What gives you the right to stop me from seeing Ling'er?

248
00:11:41,640 --> 00:11:43,040
Because you are His Highness of the Celestial Tribe.

249
00:11:43,040 --> 00:11:44,760
You have your common people to protect.

250
00:11:44,760 --> 00:11:45,920
As for me,

251
00:11:46,480 --> 00:11:48,280
I only want to protect Ling'er.

252
00:11:54,920 --> 00:11:55,760
You're right.

253
00:11:56,840 --> 00:11:59,100
I am His Highness of the Celestial Tribe.

254
00:11:59,280 --> 00:12:01,560
I will find a way to save Ling'er.

255
00:12:07,240 --> 00:12:07,800
General,

256
00:12:08,400 --> 00:12:09,260
I've heard that

257
00:12:09,280 --> 00:12:10,680
His Highness Di Yun, to save the Princess,

258
00:12:10,680 --> 00:12:12,360
braved death to climb the Sky Ladder.

259
00:12:12,360 --> 00:12:15,760
Is it really appropriate to drive him away at a time like this?

260
00:12:22,760 --> 00:12:23,360
Ling'er,

261
00:12:24,280 --> 00:12:26,480
I will refine the Seven-Colored Stone.

262
00:12:26,560 --> 00:12:27,600
Wait for me.

263
00:12:42,960 --> 00:12:45,760
I thought this curse wasn't as terrifying as the rumors said,

264
00:12:45,760 --> 00:12:48,960
but I didn't realize this treasure was protecting the young lady.

265
00:12:48,960 --> 00:12:52,220
King Kunmi, now that you've rashly removed this treasure,

266
00:12:53,560 --> 00:12:54,360
Grand Wizard,

267
00:12:55,360 --> 00:12:57,520
please help me protect Ling'er for a few more days.

268
00:12:57,520 --> 00:12:59,840
I'll return to save her as soon as possible.

269
00:12:59,840 --> 00:13:02,240
Given the young lady's current condition,

270
00:13:02,640 --> 00:13:04,520
even if I exert all my strength,

271
00:13:05,160 --> 00:13:07,220
I can protect her for ten days at most.

272
00:13:07,560 --> 00:13:08,360
Thank you.

273
00:13:09,360 --> 00:13:10,360
- Yueying.
- Here.

274
00:13:10,560 --> 00:13:11,880
I need to go into seclusion for a few days.

275
00:13:11,880 --> 00:13:13,140
I will set up a barrier.

276
00:13:13,320 --> 00:13:14,780
No one is allowed to enter.

277
00:13:15,080 --> 00:13:17,340
I leave the Cloud Recesses to you for now.

278
00:13:30,960 --> 00:13:32,960
To refine the Seven-Colored Stone,

279
00:13:33,040 --> 00:13:37,000
one must use the fire of their soul to burn and refine it for nine days and nine nights.

280
00:13:37,000 --> 00:13:38,440
But human strength has its limits.

281
00:13:38,440 --> 00:13:41,000
Everyone's soul power is finite.

282
00:13:41,160 --> 00:13:43,640
Once burned, it is hard to recover.

283
00:13:43,840 --> 00:13:45,900
If your soul power cannot sustain it,

284
00:13:46,040 --> 00:13:47,240
you will suffer a backlash.

285
00:13:47,240 --> 00:13:50,080
King Kunmi, think twice before you act.

286
00:14:51,760 --> 00:14:53,000
Grand Wizard.

287
00:14:55,520 --> 00:14:56,680
King Kunmi,

288
00:14:56,960 --> 00:14:58,240
you're finally back.

289
00:14:58,520 --> 00:14:59,850
If you hadn't returned,

290
00:15:00,080 --> 00:15:01,810
I would have broken my promise.

291
00:15:03,960 --> 00:15:05,320
How is Ling'er now?

292
00:15:05,520 --> 00:15:07,120
If there's no other way,

293
00:15:07,560 --> 00:15:09,360
she only has a day or two left.

294
00:15:09,760 --> 00:15:11,040
Since you're back now,

295
00:15:11,480 --> 00:15:13,160
you can see her one last time.

296
00:15:13,840 --> 00:15:15,880
Please trouble yourself for two more days, Grand Wizard.

297
00:15:15,880 --> 00:15:17,320
I still need to find someone.

298
00:15:17,320 --> 00:15:18,520
Two days at most.

299
00:15:19,120 --> 00:15:20,320
Any longer than that,

300
00:15:21,360 --> 00:15:23,760
and I'm afraid I can't guarantee anything.

301
00:15:23,840 --> 00:15:24,900
Two days is enough.

302
00:15:29,960 --> 00:15:30,760
Luochen,

303
00:15:32,960 --> 00:15:34,560
please send a message to Di Yun.

304
00:15:34,560 --> 00:15:36,960
Tell him he must bring Lord Yanxi down here.

305
00:15:47,120 --> 00:15:48,380
Yun Yuan, you bastard!

306
00:15:48,480 --> 00:15:50,040
Little Highness,

307
00:15:50,160 --> 00:15:51,960
calm down.

308
00:15:55,040 --> 00:15:57,360
King Kunmi, why were you looking for me?

309
00:15:58,360 --> 00:15:59,690
Please tell me, my Lord,

310
00:15:59,960 --> 00:16:01,880
how to use the Seven-Colored Stone.

311
00:16:01,880 --> 00:16:03,360
You actually did it.

312
00:16:04,480 --> 00:16:05,610
In such a short time,

313
00:16:05,760 --> 00:16:07,880
let alone finding these treasures.

314
00:16:08,320 --> 00:16:09,760
Even if you found them,

315
00:16:10,040 --> 00:16:12,640
just the soul power needed to refine them

316
00:16:13,120 --> 00:16:15,240
would be enough to destroy you.

317
00:16:15,440 --> 00:16:16,170
Divine Lord,

318
00:16:17,040 --> 00:16:18,700
Linger can't wait any longer.

319
00:16:19,720 --> 00:16:20,760
Since that is the case,

320
00:16:20,760 --> 00:16:22,280
let's save her first.

321
00:16:23,680 --> 00:16:24,740
Divine Lord Yanxi,

322
00:16:25,440 --> 00:16:26,360
do you mean

323
00:16:26,520 --> 00:16:27,720
Linger can still be saved?

324
00:16:27,720 --> 00:16:29,040
What is the Seven-Colored Stone?

325
00:16:29,040 --> 00:16:31,100
Why have I never heard you mention it?

326
00:16:34,040 --> 00:16:35,000
The Seven-Colored Stone...

327
00:16:35,000 --> 00:16:38,680
requires the Seven-Colored Spirit Bead and Seven-Colored Camellia.

328
00:16:38,680 --> 00:16:40,160
They must be put into the Qiankun Cauldron

329
00:16:40,160 --> 00:16:41,760
and refined with soul fire.

330
00:16:42,560 --> 00:16:45,360
Only those with great perseverance can obtain it.

331
00:16:45,560 --> 00:16:46,420
Your Highness,

332
00:16:47,120 --> 00:16:48,720
King Kunmi, for that girl,

333
00:16:48,960 --> 00:16:50,760
has risked his life.

334
00:16:52,000 --> 00:16:54,530
No wonder Yunyuan couldn't dodge that punch.

335
00:17:02,280 --> 00:17:04,140
Thankfully, there is still hope.

336
00:17:10,160 --> 00:17:12,480
King Kunmi, please take out the Seven-Colored Stone.
